# 2026 Gemini SDK Governance

## 🚫 BANNED (Deprecated)
- **Model IDs:** `gemini-1.5-flash`, `gemini-1.5-pro`. (Shutdown Jan 2026)
- **Library:** `google-generativeai`. (Replaced by `google-genai`)
- **Pattern:** `genai.GenerativeModel()`. (Use `Client` object instead)

## ✅ MANDATORY (Current)
- **Library:** Use `google-genai` ONLY.
- **Model IDs:** Use `gemini-3.1-flash-preview` or `gemini-3.1-flash-lite-preview`.
- **Architecture:** `client = genai.Client(api_key=...)` -> `client.models.generate_content(...)`.

## Enforcement Action
If the user or code uses banned patterns, immediately suggest the migration fix and stop generation.